comment boxed cat: concatenate nested arrays
comment enclose+cat builds nested arrays programmatically
quad assign (enclose 'hello') cat enclose 'world'
comment boxed cat boxed: merge two nested vectors
quad assign ('a' 'b') cat 'c' 'd'
comment auto-enclose: non-boxed + boxed
quad assign (enclose 1 2 3) cat enclose 4 5 6
comment string cat still works
quad assign 'hello' cat ' world'
